{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "停滯", "storyInfo": "凱瑟琳給費斯特講述了工人們二十六年前的失敗抗爭。她將關於補給線的資訊留給了費斯特與博士。阿勒黛與推進之王在行動中遭到薩卡茲追捕。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特本以為自己又會挨一頓臭駡。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他做好了準備，在心裡一遍遍打著腹稿，思索著什麼樣的說辭才能打動面前這位倔強的老工人。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳見過的事情太多了，脾氣變得比廠裡的機器還硬。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的伶牙俐齒在凱瑟琳面前從來派不上用場。她嚴厲的目光又總像是能洞穿一切，以至於他引以為豪的頭腦也不自覺地成了一堆廢鐵。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特感到了熟悉的沮喪。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在奶奶面前，他彷彿總會變回小孩子，舉止笨拙，情緒激烈，動不動說出一些令他自己後悔的話。他只能等著奶奶先開口。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可凱瑟琳什麼都沒說。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她領著費斯特走了很長一段路。在最終停下來的時候，費斯特偷偷瞥了眼奶奶的臉色。出乎意料的是，他沒有看到絲毫怒意。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前面是......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼都不是。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得這個工作室，你過去總是一個人來這裡。可為什麼流水線上是空的？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為這是什麼地方？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老工人們都不肯說，但帕特跟戴打過賭，他猜這是你們......當年打造蒸汽甲胄的秘密工作室。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴帕特，他贏了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以這真的是蒸汽甲胄......不，我不明白......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有幾回我偷偷跟著你走過這條路。那時候我明明聽見了......機器在轉，傳送帶也是。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要有人打開電力開關，它們現在也能動起來。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那為什麼停用這工作室？因為蒸汽騎士從維多利亞消失了嗎？不，就算沒有了訂單，這些機器也太寶貴了，沒有理由就此棄用。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼停了......是啊，為什麼？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$gavel1", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年長的工人拍了拍跟前的機器，就像對著那冷冰冰的金屬疙瘩發問一般。"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特注意到，這裡所有的設備都一塵不染。時光彷彿在這秘密工作室裡停滯了。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道為什麼只有我一個人會到這裡來嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡瑪，麥克，布蘭森......他們該站在那個位置。還有哈威，哈威負責盯著推進器。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整條流水線動起來的時候......哈，我向你保證，你從來沒聽過更完美的節奏，什麼曲子都比不上。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈威......哈威不是爸爸的名字嗎？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你爸爸是整個廠裡最聰明的工人，腦子裡總會冒出許多稀奇古怪的主意。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只在照片上見過他。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該見見他的。你很像他......有時候我會覺得，太像了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈威他是蒸汽引擎的專家，他自己就像一台引擎。有時候帶著大家推進得太快，快得我都跟不上。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......而我本該跟上他。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸不是被捲入了一場街頭事故，然後失蹤了嗎？從小到大，我問的時候你都這麼說。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "街頭事故......如果二十六年前的那場戰亂真的可以被稱作“事故”的話。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十六年前？！陛下不就是在那時候被......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。一夜之間，倫蒂尼姆陷入了混亂。以大公爵為首，貴族們之間衝突不斷。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "許多工廠都受到了影響，尤其是我們這些生產蒸汽甲胄的軍工廠，全部被迫停工。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈威他......那時候哈威還很年輕。對了，就和你如今的年紀差不多。他很愛這座工廠，也很愛這座城市。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天他和其他工人一起離開工廠，是想向貴族們發起抗議。他想讓公爵們聽一聽工人們的聲音，讓大家保住最基本的生活。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵......很天真對不對？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忍不住反反覆覆地想......十二月的倫蒂尼姆是不是很冷？他胸腔裡的鮮血流出來的時候，是不是還是熱的？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸他......是為了理想。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為理想而犧牲是崇高的，你想說這個吧？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們自救軍的領導者們，那個“博士”......他們是不是都會在哀悼戰死的同伴時來回說著這幾句話？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......克洛維希婭指揮官會這樣說。博士......博士在這種時候比往常還要沉默。但他們都是真心的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很可惜，死去的人並不能感覺到自己有多偉大。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於活著的人......這些安慰的話就像煙，輕飄飄的。吸進肺裡的時候能舒坦些，等吐出來以後......", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_deep_breath", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她真的吸了一口氣，頓了頓，緩緩吐到跟前。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天不夠冷，空氣裡什麼都沒留下。"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有一件事是真的。二十六年前的那個晚上，四十一名工人走到了中央區的大街上，再也沒有回來。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之後，倫蒂尼姆還是什麼都沒變，那些貴族，有錢人，都想裝作什麼都沒有發生。這工作室卻再也沒能恢復原樣。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我老了，費斯特。我不可能再手把手教出一批這麼好的工人了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來該輪到他們幹我幹的活。沒錯，哈威才該是教你所有事的那一個。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信不信由你，我從來沒有責怪過哈威。同樣，我也沒怪過你。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你必須想清楚，孩子。在你試圖帶著帕特他們暗中反抗的時候，你就該想清楚了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一你活過了這場戰爭，其他人卻沒有回來，你想像我一樣，在無數個夜晚看著沒人用的機器，整個人都被遺憾和悔恨填滿嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶，三年前，我不理解你做出的決定。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在，當我回想起那天，當我試圖去把自己放在你的位置上設身處地地去想的時候——", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我發現，我連做那個決定恐怕都要猶豫很久。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得對，小聰明是騙不過死亡的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，奶奶，我覺得妥協與順從同樣不能騙過它。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smokefemale", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳深吸了一口煙，沒有反駁。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶，我不敢告訴你我想清楚了......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也無法拍著胸脯告訴你，我們一定能成功把這些薩卡茲趕出去。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，在羅德島告訴我們，我們的時間已經不多了之後，我更加感覺到，自己肩上的擔子有多重。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很害怕我又會做蠢事。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是——我不能因此而停下。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然的話，我想，我一定沒有臉去面對老比爾、強尼、加比，還有那些在過去犧牲的自救軍成員。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你還太嫩了，臭小子。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫博士的傢伙，你看起來不像這小子，這麼大了還毛毛躁躁的。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩你多多照顧他了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "放心。;我會盡力。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line156", "option2": "line156"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我宿舍的書桌，左邊第三個抽屜裡面有一個暗格。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲盯得很緊，這家工廠裡沒有你的位置，看完了就趕緊滾吧。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別給其他人添麻煩。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......謝謝，奶奶。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在凱瑟琳與你擦肩而過時，你看到了她的表情。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欣慰，悲傷。"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，既然如此，我們快去奶奶說的地方看一看吧。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟我走，奶奶的宿舍在這邊。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貨都到了嗎？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都在這裡了。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "珀蒂先生最近怎麼樣？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說他病了。反正貨都給你們送來了，這趟交易算完成了。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，請向他轉達我的感謝。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個又一個全副武裝的雇傭兵從倉庫深處走了出來。"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為首的那個來到自救軍面前，抬起沒有拿武器的那隻手。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好，新雇主。我是鉛踝。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好，鉛踝先生。這一路上辛苦你們了。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，貨箱是有些悶。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出來以後......好像也差不多。", "name": "鉛踝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，歡迎來到倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#8$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "八隊，帶這些新來的朋友去基地。注意避開附近的薩卡茲巡邏隊。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，指揮官。傭兵朋友們，跟我們來吧。", "name": "自救軍戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4062_totter_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......加上這最後一批武裝，我們又多了幾分力量。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克洛維希婭，我們的時間不多了，他們已經開始對貴族動手了。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經從公爵府撤出來了，轉移到了更加隱蔽的第二基地，現在還算比較安全，但不知道還能撐多久。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城內的薩卡茲數量還在增多。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再過三天，薩卡茲的主力部隊就會回城。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......食腐者之王。可怖骯髒的食屍鬼。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭跟我說過一些他的能力。他以“吞食”戰爭為生。只要他站在戰場上......戰場就會變成他的一部分。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要以怎樣的代價，才能擊敗......戰場本身？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵的艦隊若不能團結一心，就難有必勝的把握。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的戰士必須避開他，這就是我們必須在他回來之前行動的原因。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們就是活著的傳說。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲的王庭......如果他們真的準備越過萊托中校的城防軍，直接鎮壓整座城市......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......克洛維希婭，你的數學很好。能不能告訴我，我們戰勝這群可怕傳說的機率有多大？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，自救軍能走到今天，靠的也不是精確的計算。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰士們已經做到了最好。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論發生了什麼......起碼我們的心是齊的。是吧，阿勒黛？", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯？嗯，當然。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在想什麼？", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在想......希望明天的行動也能像這幾天一樣順利。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_397_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g1_lentiavenue", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$escape_intro", "key": "$escape_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們覺不覺得，最近的行動有點太順了？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是好事吧？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有什麼好事會無緣無故地發生。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$2"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同意維娜。走運一回就算了，哪可能回回走運？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$2"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，這個人是不是在附近轉了一陣子了......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$2"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "shake", "power": 10.0, "times": 100.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人站在路口，朝他們所在的方向瞥了一眼。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的目光並不能抵達巷子深處，理應什麼都看不見。可他像是受到了驚嚇似的收回了視線，匆匆低下了頭，飛快地走遠了。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tense_intro", "key": "$tense_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......達格達！", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$2"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到。", "name": "達格達"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "立刻通知阿勒黛......通知全部自救軍，從倉庫區撤離！", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$2"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，推進之王。", "name